              <text>The heading to <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 24J</citation></changeable> (as inserted by <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 7</citation></changeable> of this Act) is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">relevant offence</emphasis></amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">imprisonable offence<insertwords amend.level1="insert-unanimous"> or offence listed in <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">Part 3</citation></changeable> of Schedule</insertwords></emphasis></amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
